	•	Actively encouraged open communication and collaboration, helping build trust and psychological safety.

Peer Support & Collaboration
	•	Regularly assisted team members with functional and technical clarifications, supporting smoother execution and reducing blockers.
	•	Collaborated actively both within the team and across teams, promoting alignment and shared ownership of outcomes.
	•	Supported onboarding of new team members through structured KT and ongoing guidance, enabling faster integration and confidence.

Culture, Engagement & Community Contribution
	•	Volunteered in ESG initiatives, contributing to the organization’s commitment to social responsibility and community impact.
