	•	Took on visible roles such as hosting the MAFCT Townhall, contributing to transparency, connection, and broader organizational engagement.

Respectful & Accountable Work Practices
	•	Demonstrated professionalism, reliability, and respect in day-to-day interactions, reinforcing a culture of accountability and mutual support.
	•	Balanced delivery focus with empathy and collaboration, ensuring outcomes were achieved without compromising team well-being.

Overall Impact
Through consistent collaboration, peer support, and active participation in engagement initiatives, I contributed to a work environment that is inclusive, supportive, and high-performing. My actions helped strengthen team cohesion, trust, and morale while enabling effective and enjoyable collaboration.

